				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Hard Adventures/Pulling<a name="15689"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 14 04 7:31 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>/agree Steppy
<br />
If there's just 2 mobs, I will mezz one on the spot and bring the other. It's like a delayed pull, just mezz it again if it joins in the fight to early.
<br />
Also, if there's 3 mobs, 2 even-cons and a DB, try to lull the DB and bring the other 2. Don't want to just sing mezz and keep switching targets.
<br />

<br />
Muse Famka
<br />
Order of the Rigtheous
