				<td colspan="2"><span>I used to just use mez only, but I started using lull even though I get alot of resists.  I can still effectively use lull on hard.  I ask for charisma buff every time.  I also use mez and then pull two and fade on the way back to the group.  Mez one of the two and pull the single back to the group.  When mez breaks on, I remez it when the mob approaches the group.  I do have IM3, JF3, AT3, and SM2.  I think JF3 has made me more effective and is worthy if you plan to pull alot of hard LDoN adventures.  I have only lost one hard and done 15 or so.  Only reason I lost was because of a gimp druid as healer and she couldnt keep up with heals.  Really need a cleric or a druid with a decent mana pool.
